g15message
------------------------------------------
A simple message/alert tool for g15daemon and the Logitech G15.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libg15daemon_client3-3.0.4-1bl2
  libg15render3-3.0.4-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libg15daemon_client-devel-3.0.4-1bl2
  libg15render-devel-3.0.4-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.com/menelkir/g15message

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.com/menelkir/g15message/-/archive/1.2/g15message-1.2.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack g15message-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./g15message-1.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/g15message-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/g15message-1.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(g15message)
  /usr/bin/g15message.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/g15message.README
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/README
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/README.rst

